    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Oil distilled from an inferior grade of lavender. Oil of spike is used in painting on porcelain, in soap, scent, and food flavorings.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
